\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064f\u0648\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e","numberInSurah":23,"juz":30},{"number":5908,"text":"\u0641\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0634\u0651\u0650\u0631\u0652\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0639\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064d","numberInSurah":24,"juz":30},{"number":5909,"text":"\u0625\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0630\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0622\u0645\u064e\u0646\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0648\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u062d\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u062c\u0652\u0631\u064c \u063a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0646\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064d","numberInSurah":25,"juz":30}],"edition":{"identifier":"quran-simple","language":"ar","name":"Simple","englishName":"Simple","format":"text","type":"quran"}},{"number":84,"name":"\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0646\u0634\u0642\u0627\u0642","englishName":"Al-Inshiqaaq","englishNameTranslation":"The Splitting Open","revelationType":"Meccan","numberOfAyahs":25,"ayahs":[{"text":"In the name of God, The Most Gracious, The Dispenser of Grace:"},{"number":5885,"text":"WHEN THE SKY is split asunder,","numberInSurah":1,"juz":30},{"number":5886,"text":"obeying its Sustainer, as in truth it must;","numberInSurah":2,"juz":30},{"number":5887,"text":"and when the earth is leveled,","numberInSurah":3,"juz":30},{"number":5888,"text":"and casts forth whatever is in it, and becomes utterly void,","numberInSurah":4,"juz":30},{"number":5889,"text":"obeying its Sustainer, as in truth it must -:","numberInSurah":5,"juz":30},{"number":5890,"text":"[then,] O man - thou [that] hast, verily, been toiling towards thy Sustainer in painful toil - then shalt thou meet Him!","numberInSurah":6,"juz":30},{"number":5891,"text":"And as for him whose record shall be placed in his right hand,","numberInSurah":7,"juz":30},{"number":5892,"text":"he will in time be called to account with an easy accounting,","numberInSurah":8,"juz":30},{"number":5893,"text":"and will [be able to] turn joyfully to those of his own kind.","numberInSurah":9,"juz":30},{"number":5894,"text":"But as for him whose record shall be given to him behind his back;","numberInSurah":10,"juz":30},{"number":5895,"text":"he will in time pray for utter destruction:","numberInSurah":11,"juz":30},{"number":5896,"text":"but he will enter the blazing flame.","numberInSurah":12,"juz":30},{"number":5897,"text":"Behold, [in his earthly life] he lived joyfully among people of his own kind","numberInSurah":13,"juz":30},{"number":5898,"text":"for, behold, he never thought that he would have to return [to God].","numberInSurah":14,"juz":30},{"number":5899,"text":"Yea indeed! His Sustainer did see all that was in him!","numberInSurah":15,"juz":30},{"number":5900,"text":"BUT NAY! I call to witness the sunset's [fleeting] afterglow,","numberInSurah":16,"juz":30},{"number":5901,"text":"and the night, and what it [step by step] unfolds,","numberInSurah":17,"juz":30},{"number":5902,"text":"and the moon, as it grows to its fullness:","numberInSurah":18,"juz":30},{"number":5903,"text":"[even thus, O men,] are you bound to move; onward from stage to stage.","numberInSurah":19,"juz":30},{"number":5904,"text":"What, then, is amiss with them that they will not believe [in a life to come]?","numberInSurah":20,"juz":30},{"number":5905,"text":"and [that], when the Qur\u2019an is read unto them, they do not fall down in prostration?","numberInSurah":21,"juz":30},{"number":5906,"text":"Nay, but they who are bent on denying the truth give the lie [to this divine writ]!","numberInSurah":22,"juz":30},{"number":5907,"text":"Yet God has full knowledge of what they conceal [in their hearts].","numberInSurah":23,"juz":30},{"number":5908,"text":"Hence, give them the tiding of grievous suffering [in the life to come] \u2013","numberInSurah":24,"juz":30},{"number":5909,"text":"unless it be such [of them] as [repent, and] attain to faith, and do good works: for theirs shall be a reward unending!.","numberInSurah":25,"juz":30}],"edition":{"identifier":"en.asad","language":"en","name":"Asad","englishName":"Muhammad Asad","format":"text","type":"translation"}}]}